–2
</figureCitation>
, 
<figureCitation id="849C5EA9FFC2FFF1A25AF925FEF7F94D" box="[271,285,1641,1666]" captionStart="FIGURE 5" captionStartId="6.[151,250,1283,1305]" captionTargetBox="[159,1425,202,1255]" captionTargetId="figure@6.[150,1436,193,1262]" captionTargetPageId="6" captionText="FIGURE 5. Distribution of Brachypogon (Brachypogon) ginue sp. nov. (black circle), Brachypogon (Isohelea) cuacuahuitlus Huerta &amp; Borkent (black rectangle)." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/257271/files/figure.png" pageId="2" pageNumber="479">5</figureCitation>
